article_id:437,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Issue Where the Game Crashes in Defensive Battles on Some Devices,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue in the Fire Emblem: Lost Heroes event, which started after the maintenance starting at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556247600"></span>, where the game crashes in defensive battles on certain devices such as iPhone 5s, iPhone 6, and iPhone 6 Plus which are iOS version 12 or later.</div><div><br></div><div>If you are playing on one of the devices listed above, setting Visual Effects to Basic and Image Quality to Normal in Graphic Settings can mitigate the issue, so please try that.</div><div>Follow the steps below to change your settings:</div><div><br></div><div>1. Tap More on the in-game footer menu.</div><div>2. Tap Options.</div><div>3. Select the Game tab.</div><div>4. Under Graphic Settings, set Visual Effects to Basic, and set Image Quality to Normal.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1556258400,update_time1556257326